German Economy Minister Rejects Joint Euro Bonds, Passauer Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-12-14T03:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-14/german-economy-minister-rejects-joint-euro-bonds-passauer-says.html
Germany ’s Economy Minister and Free
Democrat leader Philipp Roesler said his party will remain a
“stable partner and driving force” for crisis management of
the euro-area’s debt crisis while rejecting joint euro bonds,
Germany’s  Passauer Neue Presse  reported, citing an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
